FT  11 JAN 92 / Books: Frida Kahlo
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
'Self-Portrait with Monkey and Parrot', 1942, by Frida Kahlo, the surrealist
Mexican artist married to Diego Rivera, taken from a lavish book by Hayden
Herrera with over 80 full colour illustrations. 'Frida Kahlo: The Paintings'
(Bloomsbury Pounds 25, 255 pages)
